    `,achievements:["Created 50+ responsive website layouts","Mentored students in frontend and UI/UX projects","Expert in Tailwind CSS and responsive design"]},{id:"ashish-kumawat-dsa-cpp-trainer",name:"Ashish Kumawat",title:"DSA & C++ Programming Trainer",image:gV,skills:["C++","Data Structures","Algorithms","Competitive Programming","Problem Solving","STL in C++","OOPs Concepts","Time Complexity","Recursion","Dynamic Programming","Graph Algorithms","Binary Trees","Linked List","Interview Preparation","Coding Logic Building"],tagline:"Helping students master DSA and C++ for placements and coding interviews.",experience:"5+ Years of Experience",education:"B.Tech (Computer Science Engineering)",description:`
